data.name: UpdateObligationPaymentSchedule
data.value: update CKT_OB_PYMNT_SCH set END_DT = @endDt, LAST_UPDATE_BY = @lastUpdateBy, LAST_UPDATE_TMST = @lastUpdateTmst where (OTY_TYPE = @otyType) and (OBG_GENERATED_ID = @obgGeneratedId) and (OBG_CSP_NUMBER = @obgCspNumber) and (OBG_CPA_TYPE = @obgCpaType) and (START_DT = @startDt)
